Class AbstractObjectBigList<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<K>
      • it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.objects.AbstractObjectCollection<K>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BigList<K>, ObjectBigList<K>, ObjectCollection<K>, ObjectIterable<K>, Size64, Stack<K>, Comparable<BigList<? extends K>>, Iterable<K>, Collection<K>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractObjectBigList.ObjectSubList, ObjectBigArrayBigList, ObjectBigLists.ListBigList, ObjectBigLists.Singleton
    public abstract class AbstractObjectBigList<K>
extends AbstractObjectCollection<K>
implements ObjectBigList<K>, Stack<K>
    An abstract class providing basic methods for big lists implementing a type-specific big list interface.
